Titolo: Hard Hitter Tennis

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Hard Hitter Tennis, known in Japan as Magical Sports: Hard Hitter 2 (マジカルスポーツ Hard Hitter 2, Majikaru Supōtsu Hādo Hitā Tsū) and in Europe as Hard Hitter 2, is a tennis video game created by Japanese developer Magical Company Ltd, released in 2002. It's the sequel to the 2001 video game Magical Sports: Hard Hitter (known in Europe as Centre Court: Hard Hitter), which never got a North American release.